<h1>Move Your TravellerBooks</h1>
<%= render :partial => 'profile_links'%>
<div id="ubl">
	<p>Use this page to move TravellerBooks from one location to another. Simply drag a book from one location to another. You can change the current location of a book on this page. If you have taken a book with you on a trip, you can add the book to a trip in the <%= link_to "Trip Editing", :controller => 'trip', :action => 'list' %> page.</p>
	<div id="locitemdiv">
		<ul id="locations_items_list">
			<%= render :partial => 'loc_targets', :collection => @locations, :locals => {:loc_items => @loc_items} %>
			<% begin %>
			<li class="loc_target">
				<p>No Location Set</p>
				<ul class="loc_items">
					<%= render :partial => 'drag_item', :collection => @unfound_items %>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<% end unless @unfound_items.empty? %>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>